arStrings.szText: "Can you tell me about this geode I found in Gale Valley?"
Hmm, a lucky find! It's been some time since I've seen a geode like this. You'll need a special acid flux to get to the gems inside.
Check with Idania. She just received a shipment of some rare reagents from Hawezar. You're welcome to use our tools to apply the flux and extract your gems.
